{"tid":1699732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係只係今晚，係每一晚都要講","createTime":"2019-11-08T06:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T07:06:50.000Z","uid":128220,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7a1d8ad6b3f51845816f7e79338ddab2cf3ff601","tid":1699732,"uid":128220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:52:56.000Z","msg":"第一，今晚唔好只係哀悼<br />\n<br />\n希望大家一齊講<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢叫周梓樂，佢係我地嘅手足，佢係畀警察殺死。五大訴求，決一不可</span></span></strong></div></div><br />\n<br />\n不停講，講到自己記得為止<br />\n<br />\n第二，唔係今晚，係每一晚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望大家以後每晚八點，停低手頭上做緊嘅野食緊嘅飯<br />\n默哀五分鐘</span> 記住我地每一個犧牲咗，畀人拉咗嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n令呢樣嘢變成一種儀式，入血，入骨<br />\n<br />\n我哋呢一世人，都要同共產黨呢個暴政鬥，至死方休"},{"pid":"02069a6bcd47062aed3695873cadc1e9739dd04b","tid":1699732,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c73c332a7a6aaa4d40fe8030881622c55db0486b","tid":1699732,"uid":128220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:54:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd061e6ef12180a3c4dbe2d26fa1759a4638d987","tid":1699732,"uid":231514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a2d6b016ec94a051007c8ea26874cfad80c768","tid":1699732,"uid":128220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0529dea537efd2b06c75fe053ccb6b4f55f559a","tid":1699732,"uid":128220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:56:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61b2933f6bf1f0b5fc8f33824a26f131483c5221","tid":1699732,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,